features: NON-TOXIC DIAPERS FOR YOUR COMPLETE PEACE OF MIND: A safe alternative to traditional disposable diapers, our chlorine-free diapers are free from BPA, PVC, alcohol, TBT, formaldehyde, preservatives, parabens, and phthalates

BIODEGRADABLE DIAPERS: Created with the environment in mind, with over 50% renewable and biodegradable raw materials our eco-friendly diapers are made with non-GMO corn starch back sheet and FSH wood cellulose absorbent core

body.description: ATTITUDE Biodegradable Baby Diapers are a non-toxic alternative to traditional disposable diapers. These sustainable diapers are made of 50% renewable and biodegradable raw materials. Created with you and the environment in mind, these vegan diapers are hypoallergenic, chlorine-free and fragrance-free. Safe for baby's sensitive skin, our unscented diapers are also just as effective, absorbent and comfortable-all day long. Plus our plain white diapers are perfect for diaper cake. Try them today!

reviews.reviewText: The diaper itself is pretty good. No complaints or issues with leaking only when it was a very big blow out.Be careful however of only receiving part of your order! Amazon customer support was able to give me refund however when you’re busy with a newborn and just want the diapers you ordered that isn’t much of a good deal.
